\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid8128033\charrsid6828570 (Favorite? Perhaps, but it was the only one that would have me, at times. At the more respectable establishments, I would walk in and be greeted with a silence more appropriate to the s
udden appearance of some mythical beast.) }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid9058111\charrsid6828570 Sober or drunk, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Duncan{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 found the Spore perfect for hi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid8015585\charrsid6828570 s work}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid9058111\charrsid6828570 
. Within its dark and smoky chambers, sequestered from the outer world by myopic, seaweed-green glass, my brother felt invisible and invincible. Most of hi
