\par There is no history, no present. There are only the sides of the machine. Slick memory of metal, mad with its own brightness, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid7501382\charrsid6828570 mad }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\insrsid9058111\charrsid6828570 with the memory of what it contains. You cling to those sides for support, but make your way past them as quickly as possible. The sides are like the middle of a book\emdash 
necessary, but quickly read through to get to the end. Already, you try in vain to forget the beginning.
\par 
