\f39\insrsid9058111\charrsid6828570  a newly-ordained Truffidian priest prancing down Albumuth Boulevard in full regalia.\'94
\par \tab \'93You\rquote re crazy, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Duncan{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. You\rquote re unwell.\'94
 Anger again burned inside of me. The idea of the Silence reduced to a pathetic mistake enraged me. The idea that my own brother might utter the words that made it so seemed a betrayal of an unspoken understanding between us. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid10122328\charrsid6828570 Before this moment, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid9058111\charrsid6828570 we could always count on sharing the same world view}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
