\par \tab \'93It\rquote s more complicated than you think,\'94 he said. \'93They are on a journey as much as we are on a journey. They are trying to get somewhere else\emdash either to leave us behind or to return to a place they once {\*\atrfstart 108148226}
were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs24\v\insrsid5523448\charrsid6828570 {\*\atrfend 108148226}{\*\atnid LG}{\*\atnauthor Liz Gorinsky}\chatn {\*\annotation{\*\atnref 108148226}{\*\atndate -963149359}\ltrpar \pard\plain \ltrpar
