\cs24\fs16\insrsid9317075 \chatn }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9317075 \'93had been\'94?}}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid9058111\charrsid6828570 . But they can\rquote t. It doesn\rquote 
t work. With all they can do, with all they are, they still cannot make their mirror, their glass, work properly. Isn\rquote t that sad? Isn\rquote t that kind of sad?\'94
\par \tab I slapped him across the face. My hand came away black with spores. He did not move an inch.
\par \tab \'93Sad?\'94 I said. \'93Sad? Sad is twenty-five thousand lives snuffed out, not a broken machine. Not a broken machine! What is happening to you that you cannot see that? Regardless of what happened}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
